description: The investment objective of the FT Vest U.S. Equity Enhance & Moderate Buffer ETF - December (the "Fund") is to seek to provide investors with returns (before fees and expenses) of approximately twice any positive price return of the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust (the "Underlying ETF"), up to a predetermined upside cap of 10.16% while providing a buffer (before fees and expenses) against the first 15% of Underlying ETF losses, over the period from December 23, 2024 to December 19, 2025.
name: FT Vest U.S. Equity Enhance & Moderate Buffer ETF - December
